      "text": [
        "3372 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"لَيْسَ لِلْيَهُودِيِّ وَ اَلنَّصْرَانِيِّ شُفْعَةٌ وَ لاَ شُفْعَةَ إِلاَّ لِشَرِيكٍ غَيْرِ مُقَاسِمٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3372 - Imam (as) said: \"There is no preemption (shufah) for a Jew or a Christian, and preemption is only for a partner who has not yet divided.\""
        ]
      }
    }
  },
